metadata.name: Queen of Leaks
metadata.description: Queen of leaks or usually called Rangda is the demon queen of the Leaks in Bali, according to traditional Balinese mythology. Terrifying to behold, the child-eating Rangda leads an army of evil witches against the leader of the forces of good â€” Barong. The battle between Barong and Rangda is featured in a Barong dance which represents the eternal battle between good and evil
